                    <p>
                        Over the past fourteen years while working with some of the larger rehab companies in the industry, we've repeatedly
                        come across two things that consistently needed to change: Customer Service and Accessibility. Far to often both
                        are lost with most rehabilitation cooperations!
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col_two_third nobottommargin story-text">
                    <p class="">
                        We have found that clients are sold on being a priority only to find that your contractor's priority is themselves
                        and their share holders. We are Therapists. Owned and operated with no shareholders to answer to. We truly are
                        your partners. Living Well rehabilitation is the right choice for you! If you find your self in a position of
                        frustration, in need of quality staffing, limited feed back, or lacking interaction with the owners of your contract
                        company then its time for a change. It's time for you to start Living Well.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        You are our partner, our client and your residents are our inspiration! Your facility will have a dedicated team
                        assigned to meet any and all of your needs with the owner available 24/7 to answer your questions and resolve
                        any concerns you may have.
                    </p>
