                </div>
                <div class="col_full notopmargin notoppadding story-text">
                    <p class="notopmargin notoppadding">
                        We have spent the better part of fourteen years hearing and watching the frustrations of administrators with
                        their rehab companies.  Sadly, promises are made that simply are not kept. They say promises are made to be broken and
                        this is
